Paper: hep-th/9706001

Date: 1997-05-31

Title: QFT's With Action of Degree 3 and Higher and Degeneracy of Tensors

Authors: Valeri V. Dolotin

Comments: 14 pages, LaTeX

In this paper we develop a technique of computation of correlation functionsin theories with action being cubic or higher degree form in terms ofdiscriminants of corresponding tensors. These are analogues of formula$\int \exp (iT(x))dx\sim \det T^{-1/2}$ for symmetric tensors of rank two.